caption:
Valencia have finally restarted work on their Nou Mestalla stadium for the first time in 16 years 😍

The club was supposed to move into its new ground back in 2009, but work was halted due to debts exceeding £350 million. 😳

New president Kiat Lim has given the go-ahead for work to resume on the 70,044 capacity stadium. The target is to open the new ground in 2027. 🤩

It’s going to be incredible 👏
